{"tid":265947,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[仲未有團?] PLAYERUNKNOWN'S BATTLEGROUNDS 討論區","createTime":"2017-06-01T05:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T13:17:01.000Z","uid":104606,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aee2b0caee3ae2d5f0717e5fc2f0050a10c6b354","tid":265947,"uid":104606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:37:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://store.steampowered.com/app/578080/agecheck\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fapp%2F578080%2Fagecheck&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=aa0d33aa\" target=\"_blank\">http://store.steampowered.com/app/578080/agecheck</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/578080/header.jpg?t=1493220159\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.akamai.steamstatic.com%2Fsteam%2Fapps%2F578080%2Fheader.jpg%3Ft%3D1493220159&h=b2c38c57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n新手攻略: <a href=\"http://kissjojo99.com/archives/17254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkissjojo99.com%2Farchives%2F17254&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=92f8ba4c\" target=\"_blank\">http://kissjojo99.com/archives/17254</a><br />\n<br />\n《絕地求生》是一款大逃殺類型（Battle Royale）的軍事生存沙盒遊戲，每一局皆有 100 位玩家參與，玩家將被投放到一座幅員 80k[/url]m x 80km 的島嶼，在一無所有的狀況下探索武器並互相傷害，最終只有一人存活獲得勝利。<br />\n <br />\n在這樣的設定下，開發團隊 Bluehole 成功的創造了一個完美的 PvP 互動環境，地圖的尺寸配合 100 位玩家的分布，讓遊戲的進行不至於像《DAYZ》一樣大到甚至會讓人感到無聊，反而充滿了隨時都可能遇到敵人的刺激感。<br />\n <br />\n另外，組隊模式的遊戲更是充滿競爭性與戰略性，玩家最多可進行 4 人組隊，在有限資源的分配下與其他隊伍競爭，透過合作的方式讓遊戲過程產生許多同袍情誼，可說是非常適合三五好友一同享樂的模式，這也是《絕地求生》之所以快速熱銷的因素之一。<br />\n <br />\n當然，不得不提《絕地求生》本身在有《H1Z1》的開發經驗下，遊戲的使用者介面與畫面都非常親民且簡單易懂，滑鼠簡單的點擊與托曳即可完成取多物品的拾取或分配動作。另外，遊戲中還有機會能夠找到車輛等載具，在組隊狀況下還能一人開車一人射擊。<br />\n <br />\n轟炸區的設定也是相當有趣的設定，地圖顯示的紅圈範圍就是轟炸區，玩家若是身處紅圈範圍則會被炸死，必須盡快找地方掩護，或是早一步逃離區域。<br />\n <br />\n遊戲隨著人數的減少，地圖就會開始限制安全區域，如果玩家不在時間內進入安全區域（白圈）就會死亡，也就是說遊戲會強迫玩家進入最後的區域撕殺，直到有人存活到最後獲得勝利為止。這樣的設定自然強調了載具爭奪的重要性，也突顯了玩家在攻防之間的戰略高下。<br />\n <br />\n最重要的是，在眾多隨機設定下，讓玩家能夠每一局都感受到新鮮感與不確定感，隨然地圖同樣是絕地島，但你每回合都將面對不同的對手，不同的物資地點，走不同的路線，讓玩家每一局的體驗幾乎都不會是相同的，也讓這款大逃殺遊戲更加耐玩。"},{"pid":"5372d27d60928df80693b5ac7a65989fd21eb69e","tid":265947,"uid":104606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:38:54.000Z","msg":"我有開個RC群,歡迎大家先group up一齊組團開咪打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.raidcall.com.tw/v3/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.raidcall.com.tw%2Fv3%2F&d=hi8wbSk0%2F5PZXuKAsqUvlP6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=6a435ddf\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.raidcall.com.tw/v3/</a><br />\nRC群ID: 18644023"},{"pid":"f4c69dbcf4eb091ea2630f4885975b01874cd406","tid":265947,"uid":120020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:48:01.000Z","msg":"好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過中意solo"},{"pid":"ada6253dec2ead77618e0d387a50ca826a8f3e7d","tid":265947,"uid":60205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:54:08.000Z","msg":"lau ming"},{"pid":"682316d1d034995857f0a5c438e8cb81452e2ce2","tid":265947,"uid":104606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:56:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，不過中意solo</blockquote><br />\nPUBG今次平衡真係做得好好,抵爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7af2766a2c92e8b886734587fedb89e28ac17474","tid":265947,"uid":24264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T05:57:59.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"c6566c50f4066ebcdc8316b9819ef8a6b6fbb23a","tid":265947,"uid":14902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T10:00:12.000Z","msg":"咪有discord囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲用乜RC"},{"pid":"5a124fdf4147ab796a52dc7b80c3ea786aaf2180","tid":265947,"uid":22638,"lik